value.string: Nothing is nicer than Direct Beachfront Location. The only 1,076 sq.ft. ground floor condo in the entire building. elegantly furnished, turnkey, 2 bedroom, 2 stunning baths and Amazing ocean views plus a very large private side patio. 3 Mitsubishi zoned air conditioning units - one in living room & one in each bedroom. Owner gutted unit when she bought it and reconfigured interior into lovely and very functional condo with custom builtin's in closets, large pantry & full size Maytag washer& dryer in closet in kitchen. Kitchen has large pull out drawers under counter top range and builtin wall oven. Enjoy ocean view while you're fixing your gourmet meals in your gourmet kitchen. Beautiful granite counter tops & stainless appliances. All the floors are a very attractive white quartzite tile. . Enjoy the heated pool, barbecues & showers by the ocean... -Capture the Moment. Empty, Call for appointment. Enjoy sunsets, whale watching in the winter months and long walks on the beach...Sugar Beach IS The Best Beach on Maui! Owner's private unit has never been rented. Recent Price reduction. This is the best buy on the beach...
Nice unit. At this time the only 2 bedroom for sale at the Maui Sunset.

Maalaea Surf Resort is the secret Resort of South Maui. With only 59 units of one and 2 bedrooms on 5 acres of white sandy beach, owners have true beach frontage. 2 pools, tennis courts, shuffle board provide families with hours of enjoyment while allowing others to also have space for quiet relaxation. Miles of white sandy beach for morning jogs, evening strolls bring guests back year after year. C building guests enjoy great views of Kaho'olawe and Lana'i, sunsets, whales and paddlers frolicking. Current owner looked all over Maui before deciding on Maalaea Surf Resort to purchase. On top of location, beach frontage land and vacation rental performance, this unit has been through a top to bottom renovation like few have seen in this complex. Ipe floors, Maui's own Hue designed kitchen, bath and bedroom. Treat yourself. This Resort is a gem.

Enjoy breathtaking OCEAN VIEWS from this wonderful 6th floor location, overlooking KEAWAKAPU BEACH. This well-positioned unit offers incredible OCEAN views from BOTH sides of the building as well as views of Molokini, Lanai, Kahoolawe, and the West Maui Mountains! You can watch the whales from the living area, the kitchen, both bedrooms, and the spacious lanai. The only rooms in the unit without an ocean view are the two bathrooms! The owners recently upgraded the unit to include TWO SPLIT-SYSTEM A/Cs (one in the "A" unit and one in the "B" unit), and there are two new refrigerators (one in the "A" unit and one in the "B" unit), and a new dishwasher. The Mana Kai is a perfectly situated beachfront complex, and is an outstanding rental location. The positioning of this building, out on the point, and set well away from the road, provides amazing ocean views without road noise! The white, sandy beach also serves as a picturesque path along the ocean, and past the beachfront Wailea hotels, restaurants, and shops. Once you arrive at the Mana Kai, you never need to leave, as there are many on-site amenities, including the Five Palms restaurant, bar, and sushi bar, Zack's Deli, activity and water sports desks, and is just a stone's throw from Sarento's Restaurant. Once you spend some time at the Mana Kai, you will see that it is a truly a special place!

Popular two bedroom unit with master bedroom and bath ocean side and second bedroom and bath at opposite end of condo. Direct view of ocean from condo. Seller would like to have the option to participate in a 1031 exchange with no cost to buyer. Seller would like to have the buyer given the option to honor the vacation rentals in place.

The only ground floor unit currently on the market at this Oceanfront Complex can be yours! Warm and welcoming, every room has been completely and beautifully remodeled , including for your comfort, a split Air Conditioning system in the bedrooms and living area for those hot Hawaiian days. Decorated with teak and Koa furnishings, this meticulously cared for unit is a turn key vacation rental or second home, that is family friendly with a walk out yard! Easy access to the beach, No waiting for the elevators.. walk up access from the parking lot. Strategically located on the alee side of the building, you won't be blown off the lanai by the Trade winds! Strong rental history.... Showings are conducted when unit is not occupied. Seller requesting future bookings to be honored. Limited showing availability.

Stunning ocean views from the expansive living room, kitchen and Lanai. Tastefully remodeled with luxurious granite in kitchen and baths. You will love the gorgeous open kitchen with silent Fisher Paykel dishwasher and upgraded stainless appliances. Your family and guests will love the kitchens curved sweeping granite, with plenty of room for everyone to socialize with the chef. Huge master and bath. Lots of custom cabinetry and additional storage. Enjoy fabulous sunsets and whale watching from the over sized lanai. A-203’s views, prime quiet location, private entrance and spacious one level living area all contribute to why so many rental guests keep requesting A-203 year after year; and why the developer chose this unit as the original sales model. Onsite rental manager. Seller holds active Colorado real estate license.

Enjoy gorgeous ocean views from this rare and highly desirable 3 bdrm.,3 bath loft style unit. Take in some of the most beautiful Maui Sunsets, or watch the whales as they swim by from your lanai. This apartment offers floor to ceiling sliding glass doors, that open onto a large lanai. This fully furnished unit would make a very special Hawaiian vacation retreat . This beautiful vacation rental complex has a front desk, on-site rental manager, and all the amenities that guests & owners desire, including a newly resurfaced Pool area with barbeques, spa/hot tub, putting greens, tennis courts & nicely maintained Hawaiian-style grounds and tropical ambience.

If you are seeking a Wailea style condo in Kihei, this is definitely it! It's all about the upgrades with this unit. CUSTOMIZED is the best word to describe this luxurious 2 BR oceanfront condo. If you are seeking the very best, check out the attached video, then come see it yourself. Wailea luxury, with a Kihei price.

OCEANFRONT 2 bedroom 2 bathroom Condominium with easy access to the pool, restaurant/bar, beach, shuffleboard or take a dip in the ocean. Amazing sunset viewing from your lanai or visit the roof top with it's extraordinary 360 degree views of the outer Islands and whale watching. A 5 acre ancient fishpond located in front of the complex allows shallow water access. Enjoy the use of the barbecue area and rooftop kitchen facilities. This is a very popular vacation rental unit at this lovely complex with many repeat guests, furnished and equipped with everything you need for your own personal stay or to continue as a very active rental unit if you are looking for investment property, tile floors throughout for easy care, large bedroom with king size bed, twins and day bed in the second bedroom. the charming lanai adds to the beauty of this vacation rentable condominium and living room looks right out to the ocean. Laundry is inside the unit too! You will enjoy beautiful sunset views, be adjacent to an intimate white sandy beach and Hawaiian historical fish pond & Whale Sanctuary. This is what island lifestyle is all about. If you are looking for a great oceanfront rental or a sweet place to come home and relax, this is it. A MUST SEE! Unit is in turn-key condition and it is easy to show, when it is not rented. When you think of Maui, you think of romance, beautiful sunsets, and the ocean. Furniture Negotiable

Maui living doesn’t get any better than this! Maalaea Surf is a low-density, true beachfront resort located on North Kihei’s world famous Sugar Beach. Just 59 units comfortably spaced in multiple two-story buildings across 5.17 manicured acres with amenities like two swimming pools, a tennis court, BBQs, shuffleboard, and private beach access paths. Unit G8 is a two bedroom, two bathroom second floor unit oriented for superb views of Kahoolawe and Molokini crater. High ceilings and loft-style floo rplan welcome in lots of natural light and maximize airflow. Recently remodeled in May 2015, the unit is popular in the onsite vacation rental management program. Beautiful bathrooms with bamboo cabinetry, sophisticated tile work with glass detail accents, and spa-style river rock & glass-walled showers. New flooring, paint & lighting plus quartz counter tops throughout create a blissful beach side ambiance. Unit has central air conditioning and a brand new hot water heater. Sold fully furnished.

On the Front Row! Offering direct ocean & beachfront views this elegantly renovated upper level 2 bedroom, 2 bath, 885 s.f. unit is ready to personally enjoy or vacation rent. Popcorn ceilings have been replaced with smooth plaster. Tile floors, set on the bias, extend out onto the ocean view lanai. An abundance of custom African Sapele book-matched mahogany cabinets have soft close drawers & make culinary endeavors a dream while providing plenty of storage & display options. Specimen granite counters, recessed halogen art lighting, a SubZero fridge with two additional cooler drawers & stainless appliances are evidence of the care & creativity expended in creating this very special environment. Two inch thick louvered solid mahogany sliders separate the main living areas from the bedrooms. The master bedroom, with king size bed, has a fully upgraded bath en-suite with furniture style cabinetry, under-mount sink & granite vanity, glassed-in shower enclosure, frameless mirrored closet sliders & air conditioning. The guest bath has comparable finishes! There is a washer/dryer in the unit! Waiohuli Beach Hale is close to almost every amenity!

Real Estate is really all about location...and this amazing unit could not be better located. With amazing ocean views from the top floor of Royal Mauian looking right down one of the most spectacular beaches in the world, Kamaole Beach I, this exceptional 2 bedroom 2 bath condo has an older remodel, but has been meticulously cared for over the years as it has only been used by family. Royal Mauian unit 605 features a large lanai, spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths, in-room laundry, and a roof top garden that is just steps from this unit. The rooftop garden is a great gathering spot for whale watching, sunsets and barbeques. Royal Mauian is one of the best waterfront vacation rentable condominiums in Maui, so don't miss out on your chance to own this great piece of paradise!

Much sought after end unit offering panoramic views of Kahoolawe, Lanai and West Maui Mountain from your spacious lanai. Floor to ceiling windows from the living area and kitchen where you can watch beautiful sunsets and whales in season. Luana Kai has an onsite rental office to take care of your guest's requests. upgrades to the unit include slate tile on the bottom floor and updated showers in the two baths. This is a must see unit and has rented well due to its prime location and views.

A rare ocean front Penthouse unit with incredible views ocean, Maalaea harbor and Maui mountains as a backdrop while whales play during season off your private lanai. Grand 10 foot ceilings with full 2-oned A/C system. Excellent vacation rental. Solidly booked throughout the year. A Must See!!.

Direct ocean front ground floor unit with a beautiful ocean view, and the west Maui mountains. Well kept lawn in front. Only few steps to the ocean and the beach. Located away from S. Kihei Road noise. Heated pool, and rooftop whale watching. Currently in vacation rental.

Enjoy the MANA KAI, with the BEST VIEWS IN MAUI from this BEAUTIFULLY RENOVATED RARE END-UNIT, on KEAWAKAPU BEACH! SPLIT-SYSTEM A/C'S were recently installed. Tremendous privacy and tranquility from this end-unit, as the walk way does not pass by the guest bedroom window! The Mana Kai is a perfectly situated beachfront complex, on which over $5,000,000 in renovations were recently completed, and is an outstanding rental location. The positioning of the building, out on the point, and well away from the road, provides amazing ocean views, without road noise! This sixth-floor unit offers commanding ocean views from the living area, the kitchen, the lanai, and the Master bedroom! Watch the whales without even having to get out of bed! The white, sandy beach also serves as a picturesque path along the ocean, and past the beautiful Wailea hotels, restaurants, and shops. This beautiful unit is being sold furnished, excluding some artwork. Once you arrive at the Mana Kai, you never need to leave, as there are many on-site amenities, including The Five Palms restaurant, bar, and sushi bar, Zack's deli, activity and water sports desks, and is just a stone throw from Sarrento's restaurant! This is truly a special destination!

Ocean front complex! Rare, spacious 3 bdrm, 3 bath unit with amazing ocean views. Location, Location, Location! Quiet end unit, close to public tennis courts, pool, BBQ area and shuffleboard. Sold furnished, 3 air conditioners, full size W/D and large lanai. Bathrooms upgraded in June 2014. On site management company. Great rental history.

Hale Hui Kai is perfectly positioned on KEAWAKAPU BEACH, a spectacular white sandy beach, and arguably THE BEST beach on Maui!! This two-bedroom, two-bath, garden view unit is only steps away from the ocean, and the views from the BEACHFRONT POOL are unbeatable! Enjoy modern comforts in a setting with a feel of "Old Hawaii," with its lush tropical gardens and breathtaking ocean views. This unit was renovated in 2005 and 2010, which included new tile flooring, new bathrooms, new kitchen counter tops, new carpeting, and more, and is being sold furnished, excluding only the wall hangings and the linens. Hale Hui Kai is a popular vacation rental destination. Seller intends to conduct a 1031 Exchange at no cost of liability to Buyer. Contact your favorite Realtor to schedule a showing.

First time on the market and in the most-desired middle section of the building. Mesmerizing views of sunsets on a year round basis. Watch the whales frolic, cruise boats sailing by, paddle boarding, snorkeling and enjoy the laid back lifestyle of this gorgeous ocean front location between two of South Mauis finest swimming beaches, Kamaole 1 and Kamaole 2 beach parks. This unit was remodeled about 3 years ago with new kitchen cabinets, granite counter tops and back splash. Bathroom was also given a makeover with new vanity, toilet and tiled shower. Unit is vacant and easy to show.
